            <h2 class="login-title" data-th="‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏™‡∏π‡πà‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏ú‡∏π‡πâ‡∏î‡∏π‡πÅ‡∏•" data-en="Admin Login">Admin Login</h2>
            <p class="login-subtitle" data-th="‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡∏£‡∏´‡∏±‡∏™‡∏ú‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡πÇ‡∏õ‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏à‡∏Ñ‡πÉ‡∏´‡∏°‡πà" data-en="Enter password to add new project">Enter password to add new project</p>
